>>PINCHBECK: Well,
I mean, that's

00:48:23.100 --> 00:48:24.577 align:middle line:84%
what all the science
is telling us.

00:48:24.577 --> 00:48:25.660 align:middle line:90%
It couldn't be more clear.

00:48:25.660 --> 00:48:27.250 align:middle line:90%
We're in big trouble right now.

